Sales Dashboard (Excel)
Project Overview
This project focuses on building an interactive Sales Dashboard using Microsoft Excel.
The dashboard is designed to analyze sales performance and provide clear insights that help in understanding trends, performance, and key business metrics.
Objectives
Analyze overall sales performance.
Identify top-performing products and regions.
Track sales trends over time.
Support data-driven decision making using visual analytics.
Tools Used
Microsoft Excel
Pivot Tables
Charts and Visualizations
Excel formulas
Dataset Description
The dataset contains sales-related information such as:
Order date
Product name
Category
Sales value
Quantity
Region
The data was cleaned and prepared before building the dashboard.
Dashboard Features
Total sales summary
Sales by product and category
Sales trends over time
Regional sales comparison
Interactive filters and slicers
Outcome
The final dashboard presents sales data in a clear and visually appealing way, making it easier to extract insights and understand business performance.
